1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,209
Manji sends his apprentice, Mu Young, into the Sleepywood Underground Temple... to investigate reports of dark energy stirring below.

2
00:00:11,209 --> 00:00:14,804
It is a journey Manji himself cannot make.

3
00:00:14,804 --> 00:00:23,275
He watches from the top of the stone steps as Mu Young descends into the darkness, lantern in hand.

4
00:00:23,275 --> 00:00:27,896
The master has taught his student everything he knows.

5
00:00:27,896 --> 00:00:33,458
Whether it will be enough... is a question the dungeon will answer.
